## Quickstart

```sh
# Configure + build (Debug)
cmake -S . -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug
cmake --build build

# (Once add-cli-build-flash-debug ships)
alloy build
alloy flash
```

## Project layout

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── alloy.toml         # the project manifest (read by every alloy command)
├── CMakeLists.txt     # calls alloy_cli_init() to wire alloy.toml into CMake
├── src/main.cpp       # your firmware entry point
└── .alloy/            # generated artefacts (gitignored)
```

`alloy.toml` is the source of truth.  Edit it directly or use:

```sh
alloy add uart console --tx PA2 --rx PA3 --baud 115200
alloy add gpio led --pin PD12 --mode output
```

